  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nHere are the conditions: \r\n\"Join community\" is shown if:\r\n- the user hasn't joined the community\r\n- AND  'auto accept requests to join'\r\n- AND  the Owner Node is online\r\n\r\nOtherwise, if one of the two points above is false, we show \"Request to join\"  (ie 'manually accept requests to join' is switched on OR the Owner node is offline)\r\n\r\nSee the \"Manual Membership approval needed?\" switcher here: https://www.figma.com/file/17fc13UBFvInrLgNUKJJg5/Kuba%E2%8E%9CDesktop?node-id=2365%3A295996&t=Aj04X1c3THOVvoQg-0\r\n",
